&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Due to internal secondment an exciting opportunity has arisen for a suitably experienced dietitian to take the role of Nutrition Support Lead Dietitian on an interim basis.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Expectations of the post holder include ability to manage own caseload of complex nutrition support patients which will include Critical Care, Surgical and Stroke input. You will also be expected to represent the department at Trust wide meetings and lead on clinic audit. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;In addition to clinical responsibilities you will mange thethe inpatient dietetic team and providing support to junior team members.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;You will be supported in this role but other members of the band 7dietitainand Clinical Manager. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
